      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
        <div class="md:w-1/3">
          <div class="relative w-64 h-64 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
            <img
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544005313-94ddf0286df2"
              alt="Author"
              class="object-cover w-full h-full"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-2/3">
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-serif mb-4">E.J. Nightshade</h3>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-6">
            E.J. Nightshade has spent a lifetime exploring ancient forests and collecting folklore. Drawing from her
